code: import{Config}from"../../index";import{PING,SIGN_IN}from"../actionTypes";import Request from"../../http/http";import{query_string}from"../../utils";var Currencies=function Currencies(){return Request.get(Config.Config.Currency);};var UserStatusList=function UserStatusList(){return Request.get(Config.Config.VerifyStatusList);};var CountryList=function CountryList(){return Request.setEvents(true).get(Config.Config.CountryList);};var UserList=function UserList(){return Request.get(Config.Config.UList);};var RegUser=function RegUser(data){return Request.post(Config.Config.RegUserUrl,query_string(data));};var SearchUser=function SearchUser(data){var url=Config.Config.SearchUser+'?personal_id='+data.personal_id+'&id='+data.id;return Request.get(url);};var WithdrawalList=function WithdrawalList(){return Request.get(Config.Withdraw.GetList);};var SearchUserForWithdraw=function SearchUserForWithdraw(val){return Request.get(Config.Withdraw.SearchUrl+'?personal_id='+val);};var Withdraw=function Withdraw(data){return Request.post(Config.Withdraw.add,query_string(data));};var EditUser=function EditUser(data){return Request.post(Config.Config.editUser,query_string(data));};export default{Currencies:Currencies,UserStatusList:UserStatusList,CountryList:CountryList,UserList:UserList,RegUser:RegUser,SearchUser:SearchUser,WithdrawalList:WithdrawalList,SearchUserForWithdraw:SearchUserForWithdraw,Withdraw:Withdraw,EditUser:EditUser};
